text: Hermann Otto Ludwig Weingärtner was a gymnast from Germany. Hermann competed at the 1896 Summer Olympics. He was born on August 27, 1864 and died on December 22, 1919.Hermann Weingärtner == References == Category:1864 births Category:1919 deaths Category:German gymnasts Category:Olympic gold medalists for Germany Category:Olympic silver medalists for Germany Category:Olympic bronze medalists for Germany Category:Sportspeople from Brandenburg Category:People from Frankfurt (Oder)
